 <div class="row">
    <h4 class="center black white-text">Undertake a Perilous Journey</h4>
    <div class="col s2">
      First die roll: <h4>{{roll}} +</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="col s2">
        Second die roll: <h4>{{roll2}} + </h4><br><br>
        Your total roll: <div class="card"><h1>{{sum}}</h1></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s2">
        Modifier: <h4>{{mod}}</h4></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col s4">
        <h4 class="black white-text">10+</h4>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>- The quartermaster reduces the number of rations required by one.</li>
                    <li>- The trailblazer reduces the amount of time it takes to reach your destination.</li>
                    <li>- The scout will spot any trouble quick enough to let you get the drop on it.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        <h4 class="black white-text">7-9</h4>
            <p>You perform your job as expected:
                <ul>
                    <li>- Quartermaster: The normal number of rations are consumed</li>
                    <li>- Trailblazer: The journey takes about as long as expected</li>
                    <li>- Scout: No one gets the drop on you, but you don't get the drop on them either</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        <h4 class="black white-text">6 and below</h4>
            <p>You fail. Mark experience</p>
    </div>
 </div>  
 <div class="center">
    <a href="/character/{{id}}/" class="btn black">Character Sheet</a>
  </div>
